{"tid":362321,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(長文慎入)我懷疑我做廚嗰間餐廳有污糟野","createTime":"2017-08-16T23:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-17T00:50:38.000Z","uid":84267,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c578bcb6e6e46a4ed99eca16e502f2887557abac","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:20:00.000Z","msg":"就咁, 我喺外國一間三星米芝蓮餐廳做緊廚.  件事係上星期. 咁因為我新黎新豬肉, 資曆又淺, 所以我個職位係commis chef(最底level, 比人指黎指去做最繁復既野就係我呢D). <br />\n<br />\n個廚房就每朝10開工prep材料, prep到5點, 休息半個鐘, 5:30就準備service（間餐廳只開晚市6pm - 11pm）<br />\n<br />\n咁每個廚房D廚師都有屬於自己既section, 頭盤主菜甜品共三個section. 咁我同另外6個廚師負責主菜. Prep材料嗰時就分配工作. 碟主菜有鵪鶉, 咁我嗰時就被安排prep鵪鶉共54隻(去毛斬頸斬屁股除內臟). 一共用左差唔多兩個鐘, 跟住就prep其他野. <br />\n<br />\n奇怪既事就喺度開始. 咁D鵪鶉喺下午1點已經prep好曬, 然後就包保鮮紙放雪櫃, 晚上6點service開始先攞出黎煮. <br />\n<br />\n每日4-5點嗰時我個headchef(主廚, 成個廚房既大佬)會同每個section檢查進度. 咁個headchef就問我D鵪鶉prep成點, 我同佢講prep好曬喺雪櫃, 跟住佢入去雪櫃check. <br />\n<br />\n大慨30秒之後, 個headchef大大聲喺雪櫃入面嗌我個名, 心諗今鋪大撚獲唔通我做撚錯野?? 我即鳩衝入去雪櫃睇下乜料. 我入到去個headchef即刻屌鳩我叫我自己睇吓D鵪鶉, 屌你老母D鵪鶉變壞左發曬霉. 咁我同佢講D鵪鶉今朝先新鮮運到廚房, 1點鐘先prep玩, 點撚會喺短短幾個鐘就變壞?<br />\n<br />\n解釋完佢都認同成件事唔合理, 因為我section其他嗰5個前輩都睇住我prep, 都唔覺D鵪鶉有問題. 但佢都嬲嬲豬叫我個section從頭prep過新一批鵪鶉, 仲指命叫個souschef(headchef之後最大佢)全程監督以防差錯.心諗屌那星又要再整過. <br />\n<br />\n因為service就快開始, 所以我地有同時4個人prep. 好快唔夠半個鐘已經搞掂, 個souschef全程望撚實曬, 最後okay, 擺雪櫃準備service<br />\n<br />\n我真係屌你老母.. 到service開始, 開雪櫃攞鵪鶉出黎個陣, 我大大聲嗌FUCK因為屌你老母D鵪鶉又發撚曬霉, 今次仲要只擺左唔夠30分鐘. 個souschef知唔妥, 過黎睇睇, 都呆撚左, 跟住走去同headchef講. <br />\n<br />\n個headchef好撚嬲咁話唯有今日唔serve呢碟菜. 仲話如果因為咁而失去佢咁多年努力得黎既米芝蓮三星, 佢真係會自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰晚service之後我地所有staff一齊討論究竟做乜鳩D鵪鶉會瞬間發霉, 又唔見雪櫃其他食材有問題. 但結果都無結論, 只覺得成件事好撚鬼. 而家諗翻起個心都寒一寒.<br />\n<br />\n個日之後, 我地為左防止D鵪鶉再離奇發霉, 我地將佢D擺喺其他雪櫃仔, 結果無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到今時今日都係咁做"},{"pid":"27a4a90cc0325b80eb0a18360492e7ea1a2bf928","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:22:52.000Z","msg":"有無做廚巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33237cbc91ae9a45509705477f9c4110bfd04ef","tid":362321,"uid":9924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:28:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/072807_1e3cf63ad7f945af3ffcd825454524cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F072807_1e3cf63ad7f945af3ffcd825454524cf.jpg&h=e676e50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能係呢隻做"},{"pid":"4b92178fb5a36a7825ed63bde79539ec73913f5e","tid":362321,"uid":71198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:31:24.000Z","msg":"啲貨有問題"},{"pid":"37368ddb1578f73b756eb10dc5473fa03686561b","tid":362321,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:33:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b51997a7bc0fe826fbc1ee7c25156ebb25e49589","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>啲貨有問題</blockquote><br />\n唔會. 呢間供應商7年前已經開始比貨, D鵪鶉喺捕獲之後, 24小時內送到廚房. 好多其他米芝蓮餐廳都用佢, 都無聽過有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84077ca42fc325cb161aa6b0cadd4290cede4fe","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戇鳩，廚房咁多油煙實多污糟嘢㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n你就戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b3b0853834599f44bbae4a3396342df611ea880","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/17/072807_1e3cf63ad7f945af3ffcd825454524cf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F17%2F072807_1e3cf63ad7f945af3ffcd825454524cf.jpg&h=e676e50f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可能係呢隻做</blockquote><br />\n乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d7ab2947f249450bdc959f568ad0ec56f568d40","tid":362321,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-16T23:51:52.000Z","msg":"個雪櫃肯定無問題? 有無擺過其他肉類落去雪下試下係未唔夠凍之類? <br />\n如果都無問題你真係小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049b498186e74bc8ad00236aae5bbe9845141b1d","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:00:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個雪櫃肯定無問題? 有無擺過其他肉類落去雪下試下係未唔夠凍之類? <br />\n如果都無問題你真係小心d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n間餐廳做左咁多年一向都無D咁既事發生過, 個大雪櫃放曬全餐廳所有食材(大到可以企10+個人入去), 其他食材都無事, 次次入去都好撚凍. 就算D鵪鶉放喺room temperature幾個鐘頂籠唔再新鮮, 都唔會誇撚到發霉架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a258946260b5dbb88a8b45b5be6d5d281c5e3a4","tid":362321,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>戇鳩，廚房咁多油煙實多污糟嘢㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n你就戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個廚房都有污槽野架啦, 你真係on9到震"},{"pid":"c01df6453bcc02f848850373af853f4aec1ac0cf","tid":362321,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>戇鳩，廚房咁多油煙實多污糟嘢㗎啦</blockquote><br />\n你就戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個廚房都有污槽野架啦, 你真係on9到震</blockquote><br />\n所謂污糟野喺講緊靈異野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25f8ac6bf858303616f015c58031c8778e23cdf","tid":362321,"uid":90793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T00:50:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無做廚巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> here !! <a href=\"https://t.me/Foreverhill\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FForeverhill&d=FFjObML1d9G%2FX%2BfIzmeof8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=dec505e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Foreverhill</a>"}]}